<a  href="http://www.geocities.com/fricka_on_vallon_zek">Sig Gallery</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uastakhaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AstaKhaan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/22/02 1:57:04 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/eq/image.aspx?path=/Asta/fullsize/swedchef.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Well, as I said-</span><hr size=1> My experience is the total opposite. Players on pvp servers are in general more mature. They either know how to interact with others in a calm and mature manner, or learn to do it fast.<br>
<br>
